cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use this software, please cite it as below."
type: software

title: "Machina: An AI Agent Framework for Industrial Maintenance"
abstract: >
  Machina is an open-source Python framework for building AI agents
  specialized in industrial maintenance (predictive, preventive, corrective).
  It provides pre-built connectors for industrial systems (CMMS, IoT sensors, ERP),
  a domain model, and an LLM-powered agent layer with
  domain-aware prompting.

